            "title": "盤中速報 - 新盛力(4931)股價拉至漲停，漲停價80.8元，成交54,366張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>新盛力(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4931:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4931\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4931-TW</a>)10日10:45上漲7.3元，股價漲停報80.8元，委買8,631,000張，成交54,366張。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為鋰電池模組製造銷售。電池零件買賣。電子材料買賣。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>新盛力(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4931:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4931\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4931-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲3.52%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌1.03%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+351 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+335 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+16 張</li> <li>融資增減：+717 張</li> <li>融券增減：+302 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
